panels.name: Autoscaler URLs with Problem Status Codes
panels.queryString:
_source=<REPLACEME> and _sourceCategory=kubernetes/kube-apiserver
| parse "\"message\":\"*\"" as message
| parse field=message "* *: (*) * [[*] *:*]" as method, url, perf, status_code, k8_resource, ip, port
| fields - message
| where !(status_code matches "2*")
| if(k8_resource matches "*autoscaler*", 1, 0) as scale_action
| where scale_action == 1
| count url, status_code
| sort by _count

panels.name: Status Code Trend this Period
panels.queryString:
_source=<REPLACEME> and _sourceCategory=kubernetes/kube-apiserver
| parse "\"message\":\"*\"" as message
| parse field=message "* *: (*) * [[*] *:*]" as method, url, perf, status_code, k8_resource, ip, port
| fields - message | timeslice 1h | count _timeslice, status_code | transpose row _timeslice column status_code

panels.name: Event Severity by Resource

| parse "\"message\":\"*\"" as message
| parse "\"source\":\"*.*:*\"" as resource,resource_action,resource_code
| parse "\"severity\":\"*\"" as severity
| fields - resource_action, resource_code
| count resource, severity
| sort by severity asc

panels.name: Top 10 Scale-Ups this Period
panels.queryString:
_source=<REPLACEME> AND _sourceCategory=kubernetes/kube-controller-manager* and (*scaled*)
| parse "\"message\":\"*\"" as message
| parse "\"source\":\"*.*:*\"" as resource,resource_action,resource_code
| parse "\"severity\":\"*\"" as severity
| fields - resource_action, resource_code
| where severity == "I"
| parse "Scaled * replica set * to *\"" as direction,replica_set,size
| where direction == "up"
| where size > 10
| count as scale_ups by replica_set, size

panels.name: Successful Scheduling Outlier
panels.queryString:
_source=<REPLACEME> _sourceCategory=kubernetes/kube-scheduler
| parse "type: '*' reason: '*' *\"" as type,reason,sentence
| parse "Name:\\\"*\\\"" as name
| parse "Namespace:\\\"*\\\"" as namespace
| parse "\"source\":\"*\"" as source_info
| parse "\"severity\":\"*\"" as severity
| parse "\"pid\":\"*\"" as pod_id
| parse field=source_info "*.*:*" as source, action, action_code
| fields - action, action_code, source_info
| if (reason =="FailedScheduling", 1, 0) as failedCounter
| if (reason =="Scheduled", 1, 0) as scheduledCounter
| timeslice 1h
| count as total_schedule_commands, sum(scheduledCounter) as scheduled, sum(failedCounter) as schedule_failed by _timeslice
| (scheduled/total_schedule_commands*100) as schedule_success_percentage
| (schedule_failed/total_schedule_commands*100) as schedule_failed_percentage
| fields schedule_success_percentage, schedule_failed_percentage, _timeslice
| outlier schedule_success_percentage

panels.name: Node Utilization Average This Period
panels.queryString:
_source=<REPLACEME> _sourceCategory=kubernetes/kube/system/* and !_sourceCategory=kubernetes/kube/system/calico/* (*utilization*)
| parse "\"container_name\":\"*\"" as container_name
| parse "\"stream\":\"*\"" as stream
| parse "\"log\":\"*       *\"" as log_code,log_message
| parse field=log_message "* *.*:*]*" as step, resource, action, step_code, specific_message
| fields - log_message
| parse field=specific_message "Node ip-*.*.compute.internal - utilization *" as internal_ip, region, utilization
| avg(utilization) as avg_utilization by internal_ip
| sort by avg_utilization
